  <Icon>https://raw.githubusercontent.com/tschoerk/unraid-templates/main/mediathekarr/mediathekarr.png</Icon>
  <DonateText>The dev PCJones is always happy about a donation :D</DonateText>
  <DonateLink>https://paypal.me/pcjones1</DonateLink>
